--- passwd
ok   the walk terminates
ok   every entry is found again by name
ok   every entry is found again by uid
ok   no entry has an empty name
ok   a name nobody has is not found
ok   a uid nobody has is not found
ok   setpwent and endpwent are repeatable
--- group
ok   the walk terminates
ok   every member vector is terminated
ok   every entry is found again by name
ok   every entry is found again by gid
ok   a group nobody has is not found
ok   a gid nobody has is not found
--- getpw
ok   a uid nobody has fails
--- terminals
ok   a regular file is not a terminal
ok   ttyname of a closed descriptor is null
ok   ttyslot has no slot to report
ok   getlogin has no slot to read
--- crypt
crypt("","..")          ..X8NBuQ4l6uQ
crypt("a","sa")         saZAsH0KCthEE
crypt("password","Z.")  Z.PgLzdzPW.ro
crypt("abcdefgh","zz")  zzcHgwjUppv8U
crypt("abcdefghi","9x") 9x4JIvPW78eFc
crypt("besm6","aQ")     aQR1E1yZh1bPE
ok   crypt agrees with the host's DES
ok   only the first eight characters count
ok   the salt is the first two characters of the answer
done
